title: Does this telephone number relate to the Winterway Relief Fund (CIVD-19)?
subtitle: Financial assistance related to the issues of the Commission on Science and Technology for Development - 19 may be available, but applicants must be sure to contact the competent local agency.
author: David Mikkelson
vclaim: Telephone number 1-666-211-9966, connected to the Economic Relief Fund for the European Community of the United States of America (COVID-19).
